// node.js Microservice tutorials 
Monolithic Application --> 
----------------------------------------------------
| Request-->MiddleWare-->Router-->Application-->db |   ---> For all Feature App
----------------------------------------------------

Microservice Application -->
----------------------------------------------------
| Request-->MiddleWare-->Router-->Application-->db |   ---> For one Feature App
----------------------------------------------------

// challenges for MS 
Data Management 

 * Each Micro service has it own database
 * Services will never be able to reach the other service database.